data.title: Positional encoders
data.content:
Positional Encoders

Positional encoders are crucial in digital signal processing and machine learning, enabling models to interpret sequences by providing a unique signature for each position in the input data. They are especially vital in models like transformers where the order of data significantly impacts the output.
